WEBVTT

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.576
Our license was rejected --

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:32.976
(Laughter)

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.216
on the grounds --

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:37.176
Reserve Bank said
that we cannot issue a license

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:40.680
to the bank whose promoting
members who are nonliterate.

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:42.896
I was terrified.

00:03:42.920 --> 00:03:44.336
I was crying.

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:46.256
And by coming back home,

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:48.216
I was continuously crying.

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:50.616
I told Kantabai and other women

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:54.520
that we couldn't get the license
because our women are nonliterate.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:57.400
Our women said, "Stop crying.

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:00.536
We will learn to read and write